<section class="smart-start">
  <div class="smart-start-container">
    <div class="smart-start-image-wrapper">
      <div class="smart-start-frame"></div>
      <img src="/images/smart-start-section.jpg" alt="Smart Start - Community support program" />
    </div>
    
    <div class="smart-start-content">
      <div class="smart-start-logo">
        <img src="/images/smart-start-logo.png" alt="Smart Start Logo" />
      </div>
      
      <div class="smart-start-text">
        <p>Smart Start is our way of supporting the community we live in and helping more people enjoy technology that feels simple, reliable and easy to trust every day.</p>
        
        <p>Each month we choose one local household or small business to receive a complimentary smart technology upgrade that makes everyday life a little easier, safer or more enjoyable.</p>
        
        <p>Anyone can enter.</p>
      </div>
      
      <a href="/smart-start" class="btn btn-primary">Enter or Nominate</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .smart-start {
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
    background-image: url('/background-shapes.png');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-attachment: fixed;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }

  .smart-start-container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .smart-start-image-wrapper {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    width: 294.9px;
    height: 479.9px;
  }

  .smart-start-frame {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -25.15px;
    left: -11.35px;
    width: 272.2px;
    height: 530.2px;
    background-color: #0072cc;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .smart-start-image-wrapper img {
    position: relative;
    width: 294.9px;
    height: 479.9px;
    object-fit: cover;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .smart-start-content {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3.5rem;
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .smart-start-logo {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .smart-start-logo img {
    max-width: 220px;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .smart-start-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .smart-start-text p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #0072cc;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Anek Latin', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'Anek Latin', sans-serif;
    align-self: center;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background-color: #0072cc;
    color: #fafafa;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: #004499;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .smart-start-container {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .smart-start-image-wrapper {
      flex: 1;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 400px;
      height: 450px;
    }

    .smart-start-content {
      flex: 1;
      width: 100%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .smart-start {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .smart-start-container {
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .smart-start-image-wrapper {
      height: 350px;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .smart-start-frame {
      top: 20px;
      left: 20px;
    }

    .smart-start-logo {
      height: 70px;
    }

    .smart-start-logo img {
      max-width: 240px;
    }

    .smart-start-text p {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .btn {
      font-size: 17px;
      padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
